text: Meaghan Rath (born June 18, 1986) is a Canadian actress. She is known for her television roles on Being Human, 15/Love, The Assistants, and Hawaii Five-0. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian voice actors Category:Canadian stage actors Category:Actors from Montreal
